             was indicted for <rs id="t18210411-206-off1263" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210411-206-off1263" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210411-206-off1263" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18210411-206-cd1264" type="crimeDate">6th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210411-206-off1263 t18210411-206-cd1264"></join>, one coat, value 3 l.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18210411-206-victim1972" type="victimName">
                     Henry Arthur 
                     Broughton
                  <interp inst="t18210411-206-victim1972" type="surname" value="Broughton"></interp>
